<p>For Indian freelancers and small services businesses, Refrens is the cleanest invoicing OS available in 2026. The free tier is genuinely usable. The AI features in quotation drafting and follow-up emails save real hours. The UPI + GST + TDS workflow handles the Indian-specific tax and payment friction that global tools miss.</p>

<p>If you are an Indian freelancer still chasing payments via plain Gmail and Word-document invoices, this is the lowest-friction upgrade you can make today.</p>

